It should be noted that one of the effective way to decrease the sedimentation of nanoparticles in the conventional fluid, and hence improve the stability of the mixture is to lessen the density difference between the base fluid and nanoparticles, which is the case of the present LFTFs and therefore this is considered as a unique feature of the LFTFs.
